race.comment: Open race to close out the card. ZOUSAIN BOLT (1) has won two of his past three starts over this distance range and gets plenty of weight off with the 3kg claim. Handles all going and should be right there at the business end. TSUKINO (13) has put back-to-back wins together and it's hard to knock mares in form. Top-three aspirations on recent efforts. RUBYDOO (12) has won two from three here and may trouble the judge with any luck in running. AMENOPHIS (9) is usually thereabouts and should give backers a sight. BADDA BOOM BABY (11) gets in well at the weights with the claim and looks one for the exotics players.
